instance-variables.Text: "Ah, a lost young explorer? What you seek is at the end of this corridor, but be warned that for some it may be a treacherous venture for some. But don't be afraid; I'll be here!"

"H-hang on! It's dangerous down there! Can't you just feel it? I can't take this anymore. No one else seems to understand my problems, o-or what this strange darkness is... Just... please go back where you came from! Don't take me along! I-I mean, I'm fine, but... are you... really going down there?"
